  "text": "All tasks were performed in a soundproof booth or a sound-treated testing room as discussed in the Moberly, Houston, and Castellanos paper. [CITATION_1] Participants were tested using their usual devices (1 CI, 2 CIs, or CI plus contralateral hearing aid) or no devices (for NH controls). The experimenter checked all devices at the beginning of the testing session, and participants confirmed sound detection.",
